The first ever fashion show dedicated exclusively to children&rsquo;s clothing was hosted at the Anga Sky Cinema at Panari Hotel in Nairobi last month.The event titled &lsquo;Kool Kids Fashion&rsquo; was organised by The Little Star Modelling Academy in collaboration with Imax and the Village Market.Choreographed by Lolita Kozyreva and Galina Tatarinova, the event showcased the works of designers like Iheart Fashion, Kyomchee-Vitginie, Rayna Lynne Designs and Essential Designs.